        -: 4223:/* ======================================================================
        -: 4224: * merge() helpers -- full relational join (R merge / pandas merge).
        -: 4225: *
        -: 4226: * Every frame is normalised to an AoH (array of row hashrefs); the join is
        -: 4227: * performed on that and the result materialised back to AoH or HoA.  Join
        -: 4228: * keys match on the *stringified* cell value (canonical, length-prefixed),
        -: 4229: * the natural Perl hash-join semantics; an undef/missing key cell never
        -: 4230: * matches (pandas NaN rule).
        -: 4231: * ====================================================================== */
        -: 4232:#define MG_KEYSEP "\x1e"
        -: 4233:#define MG_INNER 0
        -: 4234:#define MG_LEFT  1
